text: Mary of Guise (; 22 November 1515 – 11 June 1560), also called Mary of Lorraine, was a French noblewoman of the House of Guise. ==Other websites== *Sally Rush, 'Looking at Marie de Guise', Études Epistémè, 37 (2020) *Mary of Guise – World History Encyclopedia |- Category:1515 births Category:1560 deaths
